Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:27.09,PW4,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.5\pos(631,176)\frz215.4}記得晾衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你在晾衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,來幫我一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拓  我搆不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那你負責從籃子裡拿出來  我來晾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  我想夾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒夾過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,做到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣風一吹就掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼下一個能夾好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.40,PW4,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\fax-0.1\pos(368,466)\frz276.9}結業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,松木和也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很努力地學習了國語呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,下一年也要再接再厲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,宮代拓留…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,請假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,宮代同學  至少結業典禮不要遲到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,老…師…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽沒叫你起床嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…不  是我又睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.48,PW5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)\c&H505259&\t(29,2573\fs45)\move(624,167,624,820,29,3574)}兩人散步小路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那就三點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我想起要和家裡人出去  來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  下次再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要我看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一共574日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,收您1000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  還要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拓  你也要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不了  我就吃這個就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那個好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下再看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,世莉架？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,躲好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,躲好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  不要光玩遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不聽話的話聖誕老人可能就不來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拓  找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,被找到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,該你當鬼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
